title: Police: man arrested after suicide-by-cop attempt in Suisun City
text:
Photo: Courtesy, Suisun City Police Department Officers investigate after a man walked into the lobby of the Suisun City Police Department carrying a loaded handgun on Sunday, Oct. 4, 2015 Officers investigate after a man walked into the lobby of the...
A Suisun City man was arrested Sunday after he walked into the lobby of a police station with a loaded handgun and told officers to shoot him, authorities said.
